So there's no hope for them and they just
go on doing such stupid things.

00:09:48.250 --> 00:09:55.820
Then we have you see many artists also of
the same kind specially French.

00:09:55.820 --> 00:10:02.390
French writers as well as French poets also
and French painters if you see.

00:10:02.390 --> 00:10:04.430
They are very left sided because they drink
a lot.

00:10:04.430 --> 00:10:10.220
If you go in any France village after seven
o'clock you can't find even one person on

